    &quot;created&quot;: {
          &quot;type&quot;: &quot;date&quot;,
          &quot;format&quot;:&quot;epoch_second&quot;
        }
Then on your aggregation change interval to &quot;day&quot; and add format field with date pattern like &quot;yyyy-MM-dd&quot;

You aggregation query should be something like this:

     &quot;aggregations&quot;:{
          &quot;date_count&quot;:{
             &quot;date_histogram&quot;:{
                &quot;field&quot;:&quot;created&quot;,
                &quot;interval&quot;:&quot;day&quot;,
                &quot;format&quot; : &quot;yyyy-MM-dd&quot;,
                &quot;offset&quot;:0,
                &quot;order&quot;:{
                   &quot;_key&quot;:&quot;asc&quot;
                },
                &quot;keyed&quot;:false,
                &quot;min_doc_count&quot;:0
